summary: MOONROOF SPONTANEOUSLY EXPLODED WHILE SITTING PARKED IN DRIVEWAY.  HOLE PROTRUDED OUTWARD WHICH INDICATES BUILD UP OF PRESSURE AND HEAT CAME FROM WITHIN THE VEHICLE AND NOT OUTSIDE FROM FOREIGN OBJECT.  ENGINEERS ON ABC ALSO CONCLUDE THE GLASS IS DEFECTIVE AND INFERIOR TO HANDLE THE PRESSURE.  THIS IS A MANUFACTURER DEFECT.
